trans-unit.target: Obtiene el tipo de control correspondiente al control <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.MenuItem" /> asociado a este objeto <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.MenuItemAutomationPeer" />.

trans-unit.target: Obtiene la colección de elementos secundarios del control <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.MenuItem" /> asociado a este objeto <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.MenuItemAutomationPeer" />.

trans-unit.source: The collection of child elements.
trans-unit.target: Colección de elementos secundarios.

trans-unit.target: Obtiene el nombre del control <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.MenuItem" /> asociado a esta clase <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.MenuItemAutomationPeer" />.

trans-unit.target: Es llamado por el método <see cref="M:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationPeer.GetClassName" />.

trans-unit.source: A string that contains "MenuItem".
trans-unit.target: Cadena que contiene "MenuItem".

trans-unit.source: Gets the text label of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.MenuItem" /> that is associated with this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.MenuItemAutomationPeer" />.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene la etiqueta de texto del <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.MenuItem" /> asociado a este <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.MenuItemAutomationPeer" />.

trans-unit.source: Called by <see cref="M:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationPeer.GetName" />.
trans-unit.target: Es llamado por el método <see cref="M:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationPeer.GetName" />.

trans-unit.source: The string that contains the label.
trans-unit.target: Cadena que contiene la etiqueta.

trans-unit.source: The name property can be thought of as the string of text that a user would use to explain which control is being referred to.
trans-unit.target: La propiedad name puede considerarse como una cadena de texto que un usuario debe usar para explicar qué control se hace referencia.

trans-unit.source: It is important to have a textual representation for all controls in the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_gui](~/includes/tlasharptla-gui-md.md)] so that you can programmatically refer to the control in a localized manner.
trans-unit.target: Es importante tener una representación textual de todos los controles en el [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_gui](~/includes/tlasharptla-gui-md.md)] por lo que puede hacer referencia al control mediante programación en su forma adaptada.

trans-unit.source: One of the enumeration values.
trans-unit.target: Uno de los valores de enumeración.

trans-unit.source: Gets the control pattern for the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.MenuItem" /> that is associated with this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.MenuItemAutomationPeer" />.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene el patrón de control para <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.MenuItem" /> asociado a este <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.MenuItemAutomationPeer" />.

trans-unit.source: An object that supports the control pattern if <paramref name="patternInterface" /> is a supported value; otherwise, <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: Objeto que admite el patrón de control si <paramref name="patternInterface" /> es un valor admitido; de lo contrario, <see langword="null" />.

trans-unit.source: If one of the following cases occurs, this method returns the current <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.MenuItemAutomationPeer> object.
trans-unit.target: Si se produce uno de los siguientes casos, este método devuelve el valor actual <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.MenuItemAutomationPeer> objeto.

trans-unit.source: `patternInterface` equals <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.PatternInterface.ExpandCollapse?displayProperty=nameWithType> and the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.MenuItem> that is associated with this <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.MenuItemAutomationPeer> has child <xref:System.Windows.Controls.MenuItem> objects.
trans-unit.target: `patternInterface` es igual a <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.PatternInterface.ExpandCollapse?displayProperty=nameWithType> y <xref:System.Windows.Controls.MenuItem> que está asociado a este <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.MenuItemAutomationPeer> tiene secundarios <xref:System.Windows.Controls.MenuItem> objetos.

trans-unit.source: `patternInterface` equals <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.PatternInterface.Invoke?displayProperty=nameWithType> and the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.MenuItem> that is associated with this <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.MenuItemAutomationPeer> does not have child <xref:System.Windows.Controls.MenuItem> objects.
trans-unit.target: `patternInterface` es igual a <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.PatternInterface.Invoke?displayProperty=nameWithType> y <xref:System.Windows.Controls.MenuItem> que está asociado a este <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.MenuItemAutomationPeer> no tiene secundarios <xref:System.Windows.Controls.MenuItem> objetos.

trans-unit.source: `patternInterface` equals <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.PatternInterface.Toggle?displayProperty=nameWithType> and the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.MenuItem> that is associated with this <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.MenuItemAutomationPeer> has its checkable property set to `true`.
trans-unit.target: `patternInterface` es igual a <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.PatternInterface.Toggle?displayProperty=nameWithType> y <xref:System.Windows.Controls.MenuItem> que está asociado a este <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.MenuItemAutomationPeer> tiene establecida la propiedad puede activar `true`.

trans-unit.source: If `patternInterface` equals <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.PatternInterface.SynchronizedInput?displayProperty=nameWithType>, this method returns an object that implements the <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Provider.ISynchronizedInputProvider> interface.
trans-unit.target: Si `patternInterface` es igual a <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.PatternInterface.SynchronizedInput?displayProperty=nameWithType>, este método devuelve un objeto que implementa el <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Provider.ISynchronizedInputProvider> interfaz.
